<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">C. ÜSLÜ İFADELERDE DÖRT İŞLEM<br/>
</span></strong></h3>
<ol>
    <li>x <span style="font-family: Symbol;"><strong>×</strong></span> a<sup>n</sup> + y <span
            style="font-family: Symbol;"><strong>×</strong></span> a<sup>n</sup> – z <span
            style="font-family: Symbol;"><strong>×</strong></span> a<sup>n</sup> = (x + y – z) <span
            style="font-family: Symbol;"><strong>×</strong></span> a<sup>n</sup></li>
    <li>a<sup>m</sup><span style="font-family: Symbol;"><strong>×</strong></span> a<sup>n</sup> =
        a<sup>m + n</sup></li>
    <li>a<sup>m</sup><span style="font-family: Symbol;"><strong>×</strong></span> b<sup>m</sup> = (a
        <span style="font-family: Symbol;"><strong>×</strong></span> b)<sup>m</sup></li>
    <li><img src="images/matematik/uslusayilar/uslusayilar10.gif"
             alt="derscalisiyorum.com.tr"/></li>
    <li><img src="images/matematik/uslusayilar/uslusayilar11.gif"
             alt="derscalisiyorum.com.tr"/></li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">D. ÜSLÜ DENKLEMLER</span></strong></h3>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">1.</span></strong> a <span style="font-family: Symbol;">¹</span>
    0, a <span style="font-family: Symbol;">¹</span> 1, a <span
            style="font-family: Symbol;">¹</span> –1 olmak üzere,</p>
<p>a<sup>x</sup> = a<sup>y</sup> ise x = y dir</p>
<p><strong>2. </strong>n, 1 den farklı bir tek sayı ve x<sup>n</sup> = y<sup>n</sup> ise,</p>
<p>x = y dir.</p>
<p><strong>3.</strong> n, 0 dan farklı bir çift sayı ve x<sup>n</sup> = y<sup>n</sup> ise,</p>
<p>x = y veya x = –y dir.</p>
<p><strong>4.</strong></p>
<p><img src="images/matematik/uslusayilar/uslusayilar12.gif"
        alt="derscalisiyorum.com.tr"/></p>
